854
01:01:12,000 --> 01:01:13,280
Dear

855
01:02:03,986 --> 01:02:06,719
"Celebrating LIght's 18th birthday"

856
01:02:08,558 --> 01:02:12,223
"This is a rulebook which was based on human wisdom"

857
01:02:12,258 --> 01:02:14,891
