873
01:03:48,538 --> 01:03:50,022
Does anyone know?

874
01:04:29,427 --> 01:04:31,040
Don't make a sound

875
01:04:31,758 --> 01:04:34,438
I brought a little gift for you

876
01:04:38,006 --> 01:04:40,008
Misa. Day 12
Light: Day 7

877
01:04:40,008 --> 01:04:41,976
I want to see Light

878
01:04:43,011 --> 01:04:45,013
I want to see Light, stalkers!

879
01:04:45,013 --> 01:04:46,947
Dad, mom

880
01:04:48,984 --> 01:04:50,037
Light,

881
01:04:50,460 --> 01:04:52,253
You look exhausted

882
01:04:54,481 --> 01:04:55,741
Are you okay?

883
01:04:57,993 --> 01:05:00,568
