While I'm here, I clearly saw my goal

903
01:06:19,887 --> 01:06:22,677
I won't let Kira go free, he drove me into a corner

904
01:06:23,190 --> 01:06:24,398
Ryuzaki!

905
01:06:24,399 --> 01:06:27,243
Let's cooperate and find a way to reach Kira!

906
01:06:27,871 --> 01:06:31,618
We can get him!

907
01:06:32,791 --> 01:06:35,962
Light...
suddenly became so positive

908
01:06:53,187 --> 01:06:55,744
Misa: Day 19
Light: Day 14

909
01:06:55,965 --> 01:06:58,661
Since he offered to do it, but

910
01:06:59,345 --> 01:07:00,997
I'm worried about Misa

911
01:07:05,351 --> 01:07:06,792
She's a tough kid

912
01:07:07,353 --> 01:07:09,224
