927
01:08:33,349 --> 01:08:34,428
That's what I thought

928
01:08:41,666 --> 01:08:44,274
Kira is just trying to make the world a better place

929
01:08:44,821 --> 01:08:48,221
It's my mission to tell the people that he's doing the right thing

930
01:08:49,131 --> 01:08:51,732
If I were Kira, I would use the media more efficiently!

931
01:08:52,829 --> 01:08:57,853
That makes you the most suitable person as Kira's partner

932
01:08:58,681 --> 01:08:59,791
That is the reason

933
01:09:00,837 --> 01:09:02,866
Kira chose me as his partner...

934
01:09:14,818 --> 01:09:18,777
Misa: Day 23
Light: Day 18

935
01:09:20,837 --> 01:09:24,387
Criminals are constantly being killed

936
01:09:25,829 --> 01:09:27,831
Even the ones they never knew

937
01:09:27,831 --> 01:09:31,653
