1026
01:15:17,617 --> 01:15:18,711
Good evening

1027
01:15:22,050 --> 01:15:22,913
Good evening

1028
01:15:23,360 --> 01:15:26,733
Welcome to Evening Spot,
I'm Takada Kiyomi, the new anchor

1029
01:15:28,528 --> 01:15:29,470
First of all,

1030
01:15:30,058 --> 01:15:32,754
I have to announce a sad news

1031
01:15:34,566 --> 01:15:38,570
Last night, Nishiyama Saeko, our excellent former anchor,

1032
01:15:38,066 --> 01:15:40,631
died of a car accident

1033
01:15:42,070 --> 01:15:44,038
She was, for me..

1034
01:15:45,073 --> 01:15:46,685
a few years senior than me

1035
01:15:47,075 --> 01:15:50,496
and one of the person I respected the most

1036
01:15:52,488 --> 01:15:55,457
It is very sad that...

1037
01:15:56,050 --> 01:15:58,418
my first job as an anchor is

1038
01:15:59,910 --> 01:16:01,621
to announce about Saeko's death

1039
01:16:06,412 --> 01:16:09,058
This feels like being on a honeymoon!

1040
01:16:11,065 --> 01:16:14,068
If I can always spend my time with you like this

1041
01:16:14,068 --> 01:16:16,184
I won't want to go back to work

1042
01:16:19,073 --> 01:16:24,131
But, if they lock me up again, I'll die!

1043
01:16:25,730 --> 01:16:26,536
Oh, sorry!

1044
01:16:31,052 --> 01:16:32,405
Light

1045
01:16:33,054 --> 01:16:33,694
Are you studying?

1046
01:16:33,694 --> 01:16:36,107
Sorry Misa, can you please leave me alone for a while?

1047
01:16:54,480 --> 01:16:55,491
I'll go downstairs

1048
01:16:56,424 --> 01:16:57,399
Dont leave me alone

1049
01:17:03,573 --> 01:17:05,533
Light, come back soon, okay?

1050
01:17:06,054 --> 01:17:08,856
I'm sorry, but I'll set you free soon

1051
01:17:23,448 --> 01:17:25,316
Ryuzaki is a little depressed

1052
01:17:26,004 --> 01:17:28,484
Yeah, because he lost all his clues...

1053
01:17:30,540 --> 01:17:31,968
You're too loud

1054
01:17:32,080 --> 01:17:33,331
Ryuzaki!

1055
01:17:34,048 --> 01:17:35,061
Please be honest

1056
01:17:35,519 --> 01:17:37,653
What is the percentage that I'm Kira?

1057
01:17:39,053 --> 01:17:42,173
The percentage that you are Kira is...

1058
01:17:42,944 --> 01:17:43,934
