1059
01:17:44,842 --> 01:17:45,320
I see

1060
01:17:47,061 --> 01:17:47,802
Great

1061
01:17:48,446 --> 01:17:49,197
I'm so happy

1062
01:17:50,064 --> 01:17:54,068
I'm also happy that you don't seem to be Kira, but

1063
01:17:55,234 --> 01:17:57,577
at the same time I lost all the clues

1064
01:17:59,028 --> 01:18:00,655
There's a vital clue

1065
01:18:01,622 --> 01:18:02,505
