1066
01:18:04,176 --> 01:18:05,735
When will you come back?

1067
01:18:06,080 --> 01:18:07,266
Are you serious?

1068
01:18:08,049 --> 01:18:08,901
Look at this

1069
01:18:13,054 --> 01:18:15,720
The red one is Kira's action before I was confined

1070
01:18:16,439 --> 01:18:17,742
