1072
01:18:21,062 --> 01:18:24,060
Are these the same person?

1073
01:18:24,065 --> 01:18:25,049
No

1074
01:18:25,385 --> 01:18:27,060
They have some differences

1075
01:18:33,446 --> 01:18:34,643
Oh, they really do!

1076
01:18:36,077 --> 01:18:39,080
