1079
01:18:45,053 --> 01:18:46,230
Ryuzaki...

1080
01:18:46,930 --> 01:18:48,088
He's got the energy again!

1081
01:18:48,283 --> 01:18:49,218
I bet you know it

1082
01:18:50,334 --> 01:18:53,271
If Kira before and after the restraint were the same person

1083
01:18:53,271 --> 01:18:55,545
THe distribution wouldn't be so different

1084
01:18:56,690 --> 01:18:58,998
