1086
01:19:03,071 --> 01:19:04,016
How is it , Ryuzaki?

1087
01:19:05,031 --> 01:19:05,789
Doesn't it give you some motivation?

1088
01:19:06,910 --> 01:19:08,871
Yes Light, that you so much

