01:41:21,266 --> 01:41:22,292
Ryuzaki will allow us

1367
01:41:22,984 --> 01:41:24,371
to just talk at the entrance

1368
01:41:25,750 --> 01:41:27,121
Right, I'll come see you everyday

1369
01:41:27,824 --> 01:41:28,564
Be prepared!

1370
01:41:35,429 --> 01:41:36,225
Misa...

1371
01:41:36,784 --> 01:41:37,867
Listen quietly

1372
01:41:41,248 --> 01:41:42,543
Will you do me a favor?

1373
01:41:45,173 --> 01:41:46,243
What is it?

1374
01:41:59,505 --> 01:42:00,485
It's here!

1375
01:42:41,175 --> 01:42:42,862
Light is the Kira...

1376
01:42:45,130 --> 01:42:46,551
He's my God!

1377
01:42:49,928 --> 01:42:51,343
So happy

1378
01:42:52,670 --> 01:42:54,275
My Light is the Kira...!

1379
01:42:57,279 --> 01:43:00,201
I'm back at last!

1380
01:43:01,990 --> 01:43:02,828
Ryuk!

1381
01:43:04,613 --> 01:43:05,713
Why are you here?

1382
01:43:06,615 --> 01:43:08,870
That Death Note is mine

1383
01:43:09,911 --> 01:43:11,857
So this time I'll follow you

1384
01:43:13,164 --> 01:43:16,002
Don't worry, your memory won't be gone

1385
01:43:16,285 --> 01:43:19,659
If you become the owner of this Note

1386
01:43:22,173 --> 01:43:23,611
Okay, I'll be the owner

1387
01:43:25,176 --> 01:43:26,444
Oh, I almost forgot!

1388
01:43:31,182 --> 01:43:31,909
Here

1389
01:43:32,266 --> 01:43:33,266
A gift from Light!

1390
01:43:35,186 --> 01:43:36,535
App.. Apple

1391
01:43:36,879 --> 01:43:38,946
Oh Light... !
He's more generous than he looks!

1392
01:43:42,489 --> 01:43:43,070
"Dear Misa"

1393
01:43:44,162 --> 01:43:49,066
"When you read this letter, you must've remembered everything."

1394
01:43:50,168 --> 01:43:52,680
"To create an ideal world together."

1395
01:43:53,319 --> 01:43:55,850
"You must resume punishing instead of me."

1396
01:43:57,651 --> 01:43:58,343
"And one more thing."

1397
01:43:59,143 --> 01:44:03,575
"do you remember the guy named Ryuzaki I introduced you at my college?"

1398
01:44:04,688 --> 01:44:07,617
"He's our enemy, L"

1399
01:44:09,187 --> 01:44:10,102
That guy is L?

1400
01:44:11,082 --> 01:44:15,018
"You must've seen his real name with your Death God's eye."

1401
01:44:16,161 --> 01:44:18,432
"Write down the name on the Death Note"

1402
01:44:18,803 --> 01:44:20,150
"and eliminate L."

1403
01:44:24,855 --> 01:44:26,253
Elminate L...

1404
01:44:40,184 --> 01:44:40,859
Damn it!

1405
01:44:42,187 --> 01:44:44,045
I can't remember it!

1406
01:44:46,011 --> 01:44:49,947
I saw names of hundreds of people everyday

1407
01:44:51,452 --> 01:44:55,411
Once you discard the ownership, you lose the ability of "the eye"

1408
01:44:56,167 --> 01:44:58,253
I'm sorry, Misa

1409
01:45:01,672 --> 01:45:03,037
Ryuk

1410
01:45:05,392 --> 01:45:06,885
Make the eye-deal again

1411
01:45:07,458 --> 01:45:08,394
Are you sure?

1412
01:45:09,767 --> 01:45:11,880
You've already lost half of your lifespan

1413
01:45:12,554 --> 01:45:14,218
You'll lose the half of if

1414
01:45:14,685 --> 01:45:16,810
I know!

1415
01:45:18,159 --> 01:45:21,043
I don't want to lose my face!

1416
01:45:21,659 --> 01:45:22,199
Face....

1417
01:45:23,652 --> 01:45:25,054
but you have the face.

1418
01:45:25,813 --> 01:45:27,250
Don't take it literally!

1419
01:45:29,338 --> 01:45:31,844
Well, I don't understand human mind really...

1420
01:45:32,290 --> 01:45:34,205
You want the Death God's eye

1421
01:45:38,676 --> 01:45:40,756
I have to obey Light...

1422
01:45:51,538 --> 01:45:53,381
Just one week after Takada's death...

1423
01:45:55,595 --> 01:45:57,198
The new Kira has appeared!

1424
01:45:58,492 --> 01:45:59,729
Criminals are being killed again

1425
01:46:00,448 --> 01:46:03,344
It means there are more notebooks

1426
01:46:04,669 --> 01:46:05,593
Just after,

1427
01:46:07,008 --> 01:46:08,460
Amane Misa was freed

1428
01:46:09,642 --> 01:46:10,232
Ryuzaki!

1429
01:46:11,190 --> 01:46:12,060
Don't give me that again!

1430
01:46:12,305 --> 01:46:14,716
Don't you remember the 13 day rule?

1431
01:46:15,306 --> 01:46:15,944
Mr Yagami

1432
01:46:17,236 --> 01:46:18,035
What?

1433
01:46:18,070 --> 01:46:21,632
Let's inspect this notebook

1434
01:46:23,531 --> 01:46:27,231
I'll ask FBI and have them provide us with two prisoners from the death row

1435
01:46:27,692 --> 01:46:30,034
We'll make the prisoners A write the name of the B

1436
01:46:30,484 --> 01:46:31,484
to see if B will die

1437
01:46:33,555 --> 01:46:37,514
then leave A from the Note for 13 days to see if A will die

1438
01:46:38,669 --> 01:46:42,585
I can't believe you treat human lives like bugs

1439
01:46:43,674 --> 01:46:45,342
It can't be helped

1440
01:46:46,210 --> 01:46:48,472
It's to protect thousands of people's lives

1441
01:46:48,679 --> 01:46:49,900
Isn't there any other way?

1442
01:47:10,652 --> 01:47:11,458
Today, again!

1443
01:47:11,797 --> 01:47:13,822
A numerous number of criminals are killed

1444
01:47:19,677 --> 01:47:20,337
Ryuzaki

1445
01:47:21,286 --> 01:47:23,445
You may be right to stop Kira from killing people

1446
01:47:24,829 --> 01:47:27,488
I'll take responsibility for the experiment

1447
01:47:27,685 --> 01:47:29,116
I'll supervise

1448
01:47:30,425 --> 01:47:30,981
Dad..

1449
01:47:32,131 --> 01:47:33,975
Thank you for understanding

1450
01:47:34,692 --> 01:47:36,513
I'll goto the States

1451
01:47:36,661 --> 01:47:38,028
Are you going alone?

1452
01:47:39,067 --> 01:47:40,432
Let me go with you

1453
01:47:40,665 --> 01:47:41,699
No, you can't

1454
01:47:42,667 --> 01:47:45,107
Stay here with Ryuzaki and wait until I contact you

1455
01:47:46,599 --> 01:47:47,811
I'll be fine

1456
01:47:48,379 --> 01:47:50,564
Others will come with me, little to worry

1457
01:47:51,130 --> 01:47:52,745
Wait, am I worrying?

1458
01:47:55,152 --> 01:47:55,838
How about here?

1459
01:47:56,261 --> 01:47:57,257
Yes, it is worrying

1460
01:48:02,687 --> 01:48:06,643
First, goto the Tokyo Bay heliport by car

1461
01:48:08,480 --> 01:48:13,804
Then fly to the Yokota Camp. The US army will carry you by plane to Washington D.C.

1462
01:48:15,361 --> 01:48:16,901
Watari has arranged for everything

1463
01:48:17,420 --> 01:48:18,024
I got it

1464
01:48:18,669 --> 01:48:19,997
See you later

1465
01:48:48,666 --> 01:48:50,501
Now, we're all alone

1466
01:48:51,669 --> 01:48:53,525
What are you thinking about?

1467
01:48:54,672 --> 01:48:55,888
Right now

1468
01:48:56,415 --> 01:48:58,507
Watari is coming here Amane

1469
01:48:59,936 --> 01:49:01,564
It was your plan!

1470
01:49:02,920 --> 01:49:03,790
Why Misa?

1471
01:49:04,682 --> 01:49:09,399
For some reason, the 13 day rule didn't work for Amane

1472
01:49:10,603 --> 01:49:12,773
Amane is the Second Kira

1473
01:49:13,543 --> 01:49:15,831
And she has another Death Note

1474
01:49:16,263 --> 01:49:18,052
This is what I'm thinking about

1475
01:49:18,993 --> 01:49:24,585
Then why she didn't write your name when she was freed?

1476
01:49:25,097 --> 01:49:29,190
Probably, she forgot my name she saw at the college

1477
01:49:29,759 --> 01:49:31,880
while she was restrained

1478
01:49:33,630 --> 01:49:35,825
Forgetting things is a girl's nature

1479
01:49:39,378 --> 01:49:40,812
I am going to

1480
01:49:40,812 --> 01:49:43,064
show my face to Amane

1481
01:49:45,528 --> 01:49:46,604
What?

1482
01:49:47,321 --> 01:49:48,718
If you do that, she'll...

1483
01:49:49,219 --> 01:49:51,064
Yes, she'll definitely write my name..

1484
01:49:51,064 --> 01:49:53,639
We can catch her when she's done it

1485
01:49:54,157 --> 01:49:57,588
Let's get her Note

1486
01:49:58,622 --> 01:50:00,664
We never know when and when she'll write

1487
01:50:01,068 --> 01:50:04,589
There are millions of cameras in this building

1488
01:50:04,628 --> 01:50:06,679
What if she didn't bring the Note?

1489
01:50:06,679 --> 01:50:08,489
She'll definitely bring it. This is a huge chance

1490
01:50:09,293 --> 01:50:10,663
to kill me

1491
01:50:14,638 --> 01:50:15,454
All right!

1492
01:50:16,282 --> 01:50:18,438
Then we'll catch her, and restrain her again

1493
01:50:18,438 --> 01:50:20,280
until she tells us about the First Kira

1494
01:50:20,783 --> 01:50:21,845
Is that alright?

1495
01:50:22,613 --> 01:50:24,719
We can definitely make her confess

1496
01:50:25,253 --> 01:50:26,253
as we have the evidence

1497
01:50:27,058 --> 01:50:29,867
You shut out the crew to do this, didn't you?

1498
01:50:30,621 --> 01:50:32,498
If she'll be tied like that again

1499
01:50:33,187 --> 01:50:35,292
She may die this time

1500
01:50:36,447 --> 01:50:38,415
I know I feel sorry, but it can't be helped

1501
01:50:48,869 --> 01:50:50,578
What's the matter Death God?

1502
01:51:03,314 --> 01:51:05,568
Ryuzaki asked me to come

1503
01:51:06,326 --> 01:51:09,552
does it mean he doesn't suspect me as Kira anymore?

1504
01:51:10,199 --> 01:51:11,277
Of course, he doesn't

1505
01:51:25,642 --> 01:51:26,591
But if...

1506
01:51:27,665 --> 01:51:29,979
I couldn't save your life...

1507
01:51:30,614 --> 01:51:33,046
If my heart stops

1508
01:51:33,617 --> 01:51:35,731
this sensor will automatically alert Mr. Yagami

1509
01:51:36,620 --> 01:51:39,167
I've asked him to burn the Death Note

1510
01:51:39,588 --> 01:51:41,880
to never be used again

1511
01:51:47,081 --> 01:51:49,672
Misa's lifespan has been shortened again

1512
01:51:51,883 --> 01:51:52,723
Lifespan?

1513
01:51:53,439 --> 01:51:54,067
What do you mean?

1514
01:51:54,523 --> 01:51:55,096
Ryuzaki

1515
01:51:56,640 --> 01:51:58,955
If you risk your life I'm prepared too

1516
01:52:00,119 --> 01:52:01,629
Let's catch Amane Misa

1517
01:52:01,664 --> 01:52:04,190
...the Second Kira in the act!

1518
01:52:10,328 --> 01:52:11,000
Here she comes

1519
01:52:33,644 --> 01:52:35,598
Yagami Light....

1520
01:52:36,326 --> 01:52:38,979
You've known that this would happen

1521
01:52:40,035 --> 01:52:44,345
Since when I told you that if a Death God expands lifespan of a human

1522
01:52:44,908 --> 01:52:45,739
the Death God will die

1523
01:52:49,096 --> 01:52:51,110
You drove her intoa a corner

1524
01:52:51,110 --> 01:52:52,761
to make me save her

1525
01:52:53,565 --> 01:52:55,716
It will expand her lifespan

1526
01:52:56,400 --> 01:52:57,400
and I will die instead

1527
01:52:58,914 --> 01:53:02,465
That's been your plan from that day

1528
01:53:03,621 --> 01:53:06,081
You'll succeed in killing a Death God!

1529
01:53:07,000 --> 01:53:09,569
You are the true devil

1530
01:53:11,453 --> 01:53:14,498
But still, Misa loves you

1531
01:53:16,424 --> 01:53:17,604
Yagami Light!

1532
01:53:18,418 --> 01:53:21,488
I'll never let you use my Note!

1533
01:53:22,909 --> 01:53:23,681
Misa...

1534
01:53:24,939 --> 01:53:26,299
Even if a short while...

1535
01:53:26,299 --> 01:53:27,667
be happy...

1536
01:53:44,158 --> 01:53:45,002
Watari...!

1537
01:53:45,608 --> 01:53:46,604
Checkmate..!

1538
01:54:11,591 --> 01:54:12,592
Did you use...

1539
01:54:12,592 --> 01:54:13,564
that Death God...?

1540
01:54:16,287 --> 01:54:18,703
Rem has a gentle heart

1541
01:54:20,897 --> 01:54:22,199
Yagami Light...

1542
01:54:25,622 --> 01:54:26,349
I knew it...

1543
01:54:26,546 --> 01:54:27,750
You are the Kira

1544
01:54:27,965 --> 01:54:29,697
I wanted to know your name

1545
01:54:32,216 --> 01:54:32,973
Loser

1546
01:54:35,216 --> 01:54:36,566
I am

1547
01:54:38,600 --> 01:54:39,818
not a...

1548
01:54:48,714 --> 01:54:50,682
Goodbye, L

1549
01:54:52,305 --> 01:54:55,204
You were the best rival

1550
01:54:55,690 --> 01:54:57,157
of me, Kira, the God of the new world.

1551
01:54:58,576 --> 01:55:00,007
If I made a single mistake

1552
01:55:00,860 --> 01:55:02,850
I might've been dead too

1553
01:55:04,526 --> 01:55:06,754
It was a high risk to release Misa

1554
01:55:07,996 --> 01:55:12,792
and let her use Death Note instead of me

1555
01:55:15,631 --> 01:55:18,697
Keep watching me achieving the revolution

1556
01:55:20,334 --> 01:55:23,133
Farewell, L.

1557
01:55:25,648 --> 01:55:26,369
I see...

1558
01:55:26,370 --> 01:55:31,563
She burnt the Note with her

1559
01:55:36,469 --> 01:55:37,427
Light!

1560
01:55:37,427 --> 01:55:38,306
You made it!

1561
01:55:38,306 --> 01:55:39,191
Misa, where's the Note?

1562
01:55:45,532 --> 01:55:47,701
So, you killed L!

1563
01:55:47,702 --> 01:55:49,576
Ryuk! How have you been?

1564
01:55:50,158 --> 01:55:51,761
I won, L is dead

1565
01:55:52,344 --> 01:55:53,589
But I still have a job

1566
01:55:59,391 --> 01:56:01,693
"Yagami Soichiro"

1567
01:56:05,245 --> 01:56:06,666
"Heart attack"

1568
01:56:08,081 --> 01:56:09,768
That's your own father's name, Light!

1569
01:56:10,486 --> 01:56:11,914
To create the new world

1570
01:56:13,491 --> 01:56:14,302
But

1571
01:56:17,617 --> 01:56:18,981
He's your father!

1572
01:56:19,827 --> 01:56:20,735
Why!

1573
01:56:20,736 --> 01:56:22,629
Just shut up!

1574
01:56:23,747 --> 01:56:25,202
No matter how you love something,

1575
01:56:26,170 --> 01:56:27,768
there's the time you have make sacrifices

1576
01:56:29,859 --> 01:56:31,503
I cannot be what I used to be

1577
01:56:36,993 --> 01:56:42,203
"Comes back with the Death Note, gives it to Light and dies"

1578
01:57:13,902 --> 01:57:14,617
Dad...

1579
01:57:24,390 --> 01:57:26,195
Give the Death Note back to me

1580
01:57:30,254 --> 01:57:30,983
Dad

1581
01:57:33,303 --> 01:57:35,354
Since we were young

1582
01:57:36,043 --> 01:57:37,609
You don't forgive even the most insignificant injustice

1583
01:57:38,721 --> 01:57:40,215
and try to be our model father

1584
01:57:41,624 --> 01:57:43,637
I respect you so much

1585
01:57:45,378 --> 01:57:47,200
So I'm sure you'll understand

1586
01:57:48,621 --> 01:57:50,148
What I'm going to do

1587
01:57:52,221 --> 01:57:53,285
What I will achieve

1588
01:57:57,583 --> 01:57:58,192
Dad...

1589
01:58:01,587 --> 01:58:04,606
I'm sorry

1590
01:58:05,531 --> 01:58:06,520
It's your time

1591
01:58:19,096 --> 01:58:20,230
Where's the Death Note?

1592
01:58:20,512 --> 01:58:21,041
Light

1593
01:58:23,187 --> 01:58:24,439
I saw everything

1594
01:58:28,958 --> 01:58:30,261
I watched you through the cameras

1595
01:58:32,138 --> 01:58:33,321
and I heard your voice

1596
01:58:34,319 --> 01:58:35,076
What?

1597
01:58:45,464 --> 01:58:46,447
Light!

1598
01:58:48,056 --> 01:58:49,124
Light!

1599
01:58:50,787 --> 01:58:51,679
You're...

1600
01:58:52,897 --> 01:58:53,745
under arrest

1601
01:58:57,576 --> 01:58:59,177
Light,

1602
01:59:01,165 --> 01:59:02,195
I'm so sad

1603
01:59:03,082 --> 01:59:03,824
we couldn't be friends

1604
01:59:07,586 --> 01:59:08,741
Ryuzaki...?

1605
01:59:11,627 --> 01:59:12,583
You...

1606
01:59:14,277 --> 01:59:15,025
Why...

1607
01:59:21,883 --> 01:59:23,245
A fake notebook!

1608
01:59:25,132 --> 01:59:26,159
Misa, you betrayed me!

1609
01:59:27,902 --> 01:59:28,882
No, I didn't

1610
01:59:30,597 --> 01:59:32,548
How can I betray you?

1611
01:59:33,579 --> 01:59:37,149
No matter how evil you are

1612
01:59:38,676 --> 01:59:39,977
I love you!

1613
01:59:43,223 --> 01:59:45,661
She didn't betray you

1614
01:59:47,401 --> 01:59:50,310
It was unexpected that the Death God acted that way

1615
01:59:53,415 --> 01:59:54,885
This is the real one

1616
01:59:55,417 --> 01:59:57,810
Amane Misa digged out

1617
02:00:00,408 --> 02:00:01,361
And this

1618
02:00:02,357 --> 02:00:05,371
is my real name, which you wanted to know

1619
02:00:09,431 --> 02:00:12,876
You can't change what is written in the Death Note

1620
02:00:13,435 --> 02:00:16,728
which means you won't die until the day written first

1621
02:00:17,439 --> 02:00:20,649
I'll die 20 days later

1622
02:00:21,839 --> 02:00:23,894
so you can't kill me now

1623
02:00:25,414 --> 02:00:26,633
when did you switch them?

1624
02:00:27,416 --> 02:00:30,133
The criminals I punished died as planned

1625
02:00:31,420 --> 02:00:32,911
Yes, on the first day

1626
02:00:33,878 --> 02:00:37,504
Then I concluded that you are the Second Kira

1627
02:00:38,427 --> 02:00:40,908
The 13 day rule is also false

1628
02:00:41,430 --> 02:00:44,261
From the second day, Watari switched it into the fake one

1629
02:00:44,983 --> 02:00:47,076
We were watching it

1630
02:00:47,937 --> 02:00:50,219
and told you a false information

1631
02:00:51,150 --> 02:00:54,708
as if the criminals were killed by Kira

1632
02:00:55,251 --> 02:00:57,408
The biggest goal was, Light

1633
02:00:57,684 --> 02:01:00,836
to confirm that you're Kira

1634
02:01:01,666 --> 02:01:03,199
You're a smart boy

1635
02:01:03,790 --> 02:01:05,339
You didn't give me any clue

1636
02:01:05,897 --> 02:01:06,921
So I decided

1637
02:01:08,910 --> 02:01:10,868
to give up my own life

1638
02:01:11,674 --> 02:01:15,128
This plan couldn't succeed without Mr. Yagami's cooperation

1639
02:01:16,363 --> 02:01:19,061
He is a very sincere person. At first he refused to do it

1640
02:01:19,873 --> 02:01:22,199
But when I showed him my name written in the Note

1641
02:01:22,654 --> 02:01:24,973
